## Requirements

### REQ-CLM-001
- **Status**: Draft
- **Description**: Independent claims must be self-contained and define the invention completely

### REQ-SPEC-001
- **Status**: Draft
- **Description**: Specification must enable a person of ordinary skill to make and use the invention

### REQ-FIG-001
- **Status**: Draft
- **Description**: All figures must be numbered and referenced in the specification

{% elif project.type.value == 'legal-compliance' %}
